      "id": "9695",
      "title": "The Hollow",
      "description": "Commemorating the 200th anniversary of Washington Irving’s “The Legend of Sleepy Hollow,”  The Hollow  is a modern take on the timeless story of Ichabod Crane and the Headless Horseman. When three 6th graders at Sleepy Hollow Middle School stumble upon a real-life ghost story, they find themselves on the trail of the Headless Horseman himself. Is he truly a terrifying ghoul, or has he been misunderstood for all these years? The Hollow is produced by Gen-Z Media. For more great Gen-Z podcasts visit http://gzmshows.com or follow us on Twitter and Facebook and Instagram .",
